00:38:39.120 --> 00:38:40.800
Don't worry. It won't affect the mission.

00:38:41.000 --> 00:38:41.760
Okay.

00:38:45.120 --> 00:38:46.520
I said I'm fine.

00:38:49.040 --> 00:38:50.240
Look at you.

00:38:50.240 --> 00:38:51.600
